  "body": "Add async version of wrap_tool_call for middleware with checks for passed async function and `await handler`. Tested and verified with my own agent through the following snippet:\r\n```\r\n@awrap_tool_call\r\nasync def handle_tool_errors(request, handler):\r\n    try:\r\n        return await handler(request)\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return ToolMessage(\r\n            content=f\"Tool error: Please check your input and try again. ({str(e)})\",\r\n            tool_call_id=request.tool_call[\"id\"],\r\n            is_error=True\r\n        )\r\n```\r\nLinkedIn: https://linkedin.com/in/astroa7m\r\n",
